* {{note label|Note|b|b}} Steven Zaloga (2015) wrote that the 3rd Mechanized Crops had 672 tanks, of which were 50 [[T-34]]s and with two divisions consisted of 78 heavy [[KV tank|KV-1s]] tanks.{{Sfn|Zaloga|2015|p=102}}
* {{note label|Note|c|c}} Steven Zaloga (2015) wrote that the 12th Mechanized Crops had 730 tanks available.{{Sfn|Zaloga|2015|p=102}}
